# C++ Testing Framework

## Requirement

All C++ projects SHALL use Google Test (gtest) as the unit testing framework.

Test files SHALL be organized in a `tests/` directory or follow a consistent naming convention (e.g., `*_test.cpp`, `test_*.cpp`).
